    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2), featuring the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six paired with a 6-speed manual transaxle. This example boasts a documented service history, including a proactive IMS bearing ceramic upgrade and a fresh rear main seal. The chassis retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with original Bilstein dampers and a rigid multi-link rear suspension. The exterior presents in flawless Arctic Silver Metallic with all original VIN tags intact, while the interior remains in showroom condition with no bolster wear on the leather sport seats. An analog driver\u2019s car with a perfectly linear power band and a precise short-throw shifter.",
